casebody.head_matter:
Robert A. DiGIORGIO, petitioner,
v.
SECURITIES AND EXCHANGE COMMISSION.
No. 16-8119.
Supreme Court of the United States
June 5, 2017.
Motion of petitioner for reconsideration of order denying leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. The order entered April 17, 2017, is vacated. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eleventh Circuit denied.
